🛒 ShopEasy - eCommerce Web Application
📌 Overview
ShopEasy is a full-stack eCommerce web application that allows users to browse products, add items to cart, and manage purchases seamlessly. It provides a smooth and responsive shopping experience.
________________________________________
🚀 Features
•	🛍️ Product listing and browsing

•	🛒 Add to cart and remove items

•	💳 Checkout system (basic)

•	📱 Responsive design
________________________________________
🛠️ Tech Stack
•	Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

•	Backend: Node.js, Express.js

•	Database: (if used, mention MongoDB / JSON)
________________________________________
⚙️ Installation & Setup
1.	Clone the repository
        https://github.com/552006preet/Code_Alpha__Ecommerce-store
2.	Navigate to project folder
cd ecommerce
3.	Install dependencies
npm install
4.	Run the server
node server.js
